    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and handles like a dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure! Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
