    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving masterpiece. At its heart lies the S54B32 inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock. This specimen has been proactively maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup that provides the telepathic steering feedback this platform is renowned for. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and cooling system are in peak operating condition, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
